{"lemma": "سَوْأَةٌ", "slug": "سَوْأَةٌ", "root": "س.#.#", "root_slug": "س-_-_", "root_link": "/words/roots/س-_-_", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": false}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n21347"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "unevenness", "fa": "ناهمواری", "ur": "ناہمواری", "tr": "düzgünlük", "id": "ketidakrataan", "bn": "অসমতা", "es": "desnivel", "fr": "irrégularité", "de": "Unebenheit", "ru": "неровность", "zh": "不平整"}, "definition": null, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n21347", "headword_ar": "سوّاهُ", "root": "swY", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, M, &c.,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tasowiyapN", "text_ar": "تَسْوِيَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made it equal, equable, uniform, even, level, flat, plane"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "plain;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * M, MA, Msb, K;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "equal in respect of elevation"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of depression;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Er-Rághib, TA;) [and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "straight, right, direct,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "rightly directed;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see its quasi-pass. 8;)] and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AswAhu", "text_ar": "اسواهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the same; (M, K;) namely, a place, (Msb, K,) or a thing, (S, M, Er-Rághib, TA,) or an uneven, or a crooked, thing. (Mgh.) It is said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faA^amara biAlxirabi fasuw~iyato", "text_ar": "فَاَمَرَ بِالخِرَبِ فَسُوِّيَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And he gave orders respecting the ruins, and they were levelled"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xrb", "text_ar": "خرب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And in another trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~ayonaA EalaY ruqay~apa", "text_ar": "سَوَّيْنَا عَلَى رُقَيَّةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "We buried Ru- keiyeh, and made the earth of the grave even,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "level, over her."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh.) [Hence also,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "suw~iyto", "text_ar": "سُوِّيتْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ealayohi AlA^aroDu", "text_ar": "عَلَيْهِ الاَرْضُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": see 8. And hence the saying in the Kur [iv. 45],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "luwo tusaw~aY bihimu A@loA^aroDu", "text_ar": "لُوْ تُسَوَّى بِهِمُ ا@لْاَرْضُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "That they were buried, and that the ground were made level over them;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * Bd;)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bi", "text_ar": "بِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "being here syn. with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY", "text_ar": "عَلَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "b", "text_ar": "ب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":) or the meaning is,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that they became like the dust of the earth;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, Jel;) thus expl. by Th; (M;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that they had not been created, and that they and the earth were alike."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd.) [Hence also,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "balaY qaAdiriyna", "text_ar": "بَلَى قَادِرِينَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY A^ano nusaw~iYa banaAnahu", "text_ar": "عَلَى اَنْ نُسَوِّىَ بَنَانَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the same [lxxv. 4], is said to mean ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Yea: we are able"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to make his hand like the foot of the camel, without fingers:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to make his fingers uniform, of one measure"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "size:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) or the meaning is,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "we are able to put together the bones of his fingers"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "consistently"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as they were."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd, Jel.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayona", "text_ar": "بَيْنَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hat~aY A_i*aA saAwaY", "text_ar": "حَتَّى اـِذَا سَاوَى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@lS~adafayoni", "text_ar": "ا@لصَّدَفَيْنِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the Kur [xviii. 95], means"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~aY", "text_ar": "سَوَّى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayonahumaA", "text_ar": "بَيْنَهُمَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Until, when he had made the space between the two sides of the mountains even,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "level,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by filling it up]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made it uniform, equal,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "consimilar,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "with another thing.] One says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~ayotuhu bihi", "text_ar": "سَوَّيْتُهُ بِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, K,) inf. n. as above; (K;) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bh", "text_ar": "به"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAwayotuhu", "text_ar": "سَاوَيْتُهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, * TA, TK,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bh", "text_ar": "به"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asowayotuhu", "text_ar": "اَسْوَيْتُهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I made it uniform,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "equal, with it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "like it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K, TA:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAwayotu", "text_ar": "سَاوَيْتُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA bi*aAka", "text_ar": "هٰذَا بِذَاكَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I raised this so as to make it equal in measure,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "quantity,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "amount, with that."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~ayotu bayonahumaA", "text_ar": "سَوَّيْتُ بَيْنَهُمَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAwayotu", "text_ar": "سَاوَيْتُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, M, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I made them uniform,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "equal, each with the other;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "like each other."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K, TA.) ―         -b3-  [And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made it symmetrical"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "symmetrically, by,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with, a just adaptation of its component parts; made it congruous"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "consistent in its several parts,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with congruity"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "consistency in its several parts: he made it, formed it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fashioned"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 1477}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it, in a suitable manner: he made it to be adapted,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "so as to be adapted, to the exigencies,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "requirements, of its case,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of wisdom: he made it complete,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in a complete manner; completed it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "completed its make: he made it right"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "good,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in a right"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "good manner; rectified it; adjusted it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "put it into a right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "good, state."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] In the Kur xxxii. 8, it means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made him symmetrical"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "symmetrically"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by the fit,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "suitable, formation of his members."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd,) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~ayotuhu", "text_ar": "سَوَّيْتُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the same, xv. 29 and xxxviii. 72,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I made his creation symmetrical:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I completed him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "made him complete."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Jel.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~aY", "text_ar": "سَوَّى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the same, lxxxvii. 2,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "what He created"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "congruous"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "consistent in the several parts."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Jel.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@l~a*iY xalaqaka fasaw~aAka", "text_ar": "ا@لَّذِى خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّاكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the same [lxxxii. 7], means ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Who created thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and made thy creation to be adapted to the exigencies,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "requirements, of wisdom."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wanafosK wamaA", "text_ar": "وَنَفْسٍ وَمَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~aAhaA", "text_ar": "سَوَّاهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the same, [xci. 7, means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "By a soul and what made it to be adapted to its exigencies,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e., to the performance of its functions, for it] is indicative of the faculties of the soul: this explanation is more proper than that which makes"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mA", "text_ar": "ما"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to mean ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Him who,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e.] God. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rafaEa samokahaA fasaw~aAhaA", "text_ar": "رَفَعَ سَمْكَهَا فَسَوَّاهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the same, lxxix. 28, means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He hath raised high"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "its canopy,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the measure of its elevation from the earth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "its thickness upwards, and made it symmetrical,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "even,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "completed it by adorning it with the stars,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd, TA, *) agreeably with what is said in the Kur xxxvii. 6, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and by means of the revolvings"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thereof"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "&c.:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "from the saying next following. (Bd.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sw~Y", "text_ar": "سوّى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN A^amorahu", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ اَمْرَهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one rectified,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "adjusted, his affair;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "put it into a right,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "good, state."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd in lxxix. 28.) [Hence,] one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~i walaA", "text_ar": "سَوِّ وَلَا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tusaw~iy^o", "text_ar": "تُسَوِّيْ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Rectify thou, and do not corrupt,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mar."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A and TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "swA^", "text_ar": "سوا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) [One says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sw~Y", "text_ar": "سوّى"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlT~aEaAma", "text_ar": "الطَّعَامَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He cooked the food thoroughly:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "see 8 as its quasi-pass.] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sw~Y fulaAnN manoSuwbapF", "text_ar": "سوّى فُلَانٌ مَنْصُوبَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one framed a stratagem,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "plot"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nSb", "text_ar": "نصب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~aY", "text_ar": "سَوَّى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as an intrans. verb, if not a mistranscription for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "suw~iYa", "text_ar": "سُوِّىَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], inf. n. as above: see 8.       -A3-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "suw~iYa", "text_ar": "سُوِّىَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [app. for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "suw~iy^a", "text_ar": "سُوِّيَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",] inf. n. as above, signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, altered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for the worse"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "guy~ira", "text_ar": "غُيِّرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["K", "Msb", "TA", "M", "S", "Bd"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}